  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed development does not adequately assess the development's impact on proximity to the natural bank of the River Rom, contrary to Policy 31 of the Havering Local Plan, Policy SI 12 of the London Plan 2021 and the guidance contained in the National Planning Policy Framework.",
    "Insufficient information has been provided with the application to demonstrate satisfactorily that any adverse amenity impacts on nearby residents associated with the proposed front, side and rear extension in terms of noise and disturbance would be acceptable. The development would accordingly be contrary to Local Plan Policy 7 and Policy D14 of the London Plan.",
    "Insufficient information has been provided with the application to demonstrate satisfactorily that any adverse parking and highways impacts associated with the proposed front, side and rear extension erection would be acceptable. The development would accordingly be contrary to Local Plan Policy 24 and Policy T6 of the London Plan.",
    "In the event that this application is allowed through the appeals process, the proposal would be liable for the following CIL contributions:",
    "Mayoral CIL (MCIL2) contribution of £2,500 (x £25 per sqm).",
    "Havering CIL (HCIL) contribution of £125,000 (x £125 per sqm)",
    "Each contribution would be subject to indexation.",
